song.title: Among The Stars
song.info:
Lamb wrote: The original title of this song is of course "among the stars", but because of fact that I have decided to put it into "day" part of "autumn leaf" (see Pouet link) playlist, I have temporarily changed the title to "among the clouds" to keep some logical consistency. "Stars" at a bright autumn morning seemed a bit out of the spot for me.
